entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: The kidnapped victims have been freed.  All that is left is to deal with the leader.
entries.journal_entry_description: Rescue the kidnapped victims from the cave.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: The cave-dwellers have rigged a barrier field around each of their victims' cages. Rough the kidnappers up until you find the keycode to turn off the first cage's field.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Recover the Keycode to the First Cage
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The cage has a terminal next to it.  Use the code you got to turn off the trap.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Turn Off the First Cage's Trap
